  ('social-worker-moex-02075', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-106-7c9828ae', 'sub-social-worker-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何者不是醫務社會工作專業價值和機構之間的衝突？', '["醫師主導性強，社工重視案主自決", "醫療團隊中的各種專業，以醫師為主要領導者", "醫師重視延續生命，社工重視案主生活品質", "醫師比較不重視案主情緒反應，社工重視案主情緒反應"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:11+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5823691fd765", "answer_pdf_sha1": "9eafd9800cdf", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106030", "c": "107", "s": "0601", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 13, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-02076', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-106-7c9828ae', 'sub-social-worker-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '以下身心障礙觀點的論述中，何者論述有誤？', '["文化觀點下的身心障礙是指社會結構與社會的價值觀形塑身心障礙", "目前身心障礙觀點需了解身體傷殘的來源，以醫師觀點為主", "社會性障礙造成社會排除和歧視，功能性障礙是身體傷殘引起", "「國際健康功能與身心障礙分類系統」（International Classification of Functioning, Disability and Health， 簡稱ICF）是生物心理社會模式，障礙與功能是健康狀態與環境因素交互作用下的結果"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:11+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5823691fd765", "answer_pdf_sha1": "9eafd9800cdf", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106030", "c": "107", "s": "0601", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 14, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-02077', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-106-7c9828ae', 'sub-social-worker-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '社會功能（social functioning）評估是指在日常生活中，案主各種社會經驗裡達成滿意關係的活動。請問 下面那一項不是社會功能評估內容？', '["家庭關係", "家務能力", "就學經驗", "工作史"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:11+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5823691fd765", "answer_pdf_sha1": "9eafd9800cdf", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106030", "c": "107", "s": "0601", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 15, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-02078', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-106-7c9828ae', 'sub-social-worker-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '若以理論所涵蓋之問題範疇區分，試問下列那一種理論與其他理論不同？', '["基變理論", "認知行為理論", "心理暨社會派", "任務中心理論"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:11+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5823691fd765", "answer_pdf_sha1": "9eafd9800cdf", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106030", "c": "107", "s": "0601", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 16, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-02079', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-106-7c9828ae', 'sub-social-worker-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '同理心可分為五個層次，試問以下這句話「對於是否能搬進去老人公寓裡的審核進度緩慢，你似乎感到 非常生氣，而且對於是否被核准的可能性感到懷疑？」屬於那一個層次？', '["低層次的同理反應", "中低層次的同理反應", "可替換或循環的同理反應", "中高層次的同理反應"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:11+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5823691fd765", "answer_pdf_sha1": "9eafd9800cdf", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106030", "c": "107", "s": "0601", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 17, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-02080', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-106-7c9828ae', 'sub-social-worker-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關Rothman提出之社區組織模式─社會計畫，下列敘述何者錯誤？', '["社會計畫的行動目標強調社區自助、社區能量之整合，屬於過程目標", "社會計畫假設社區存在實質的社會問題", "社會工作者扮演方案執行者或催化者", "社會計畫是一種有計畫的變遷（planned change），透過客觀的分析各種不同的情境，進行決策，最後 訂定出一個最佳的方案"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:11+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5823691fd765", "answer_pdf_sha1": "9eafd9800cdf", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106030", "c": "107", "s": "0601", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 18, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL)
